name: COLE BLACKWELL
description: A while ago i decided to design a family of 5 members called the Black-Well family. A first glance make people to keep themselves far from them. sad and fallen eyes with lips that seems to have a smile on them forever. the first character i drew from this family is "Cole Black-Well", a 58 years old father that has three children, two sons and a daughter. a father with white gray hair and a relatively wrinkled skin that is slowly stepping into the world of 60. in childhood, he was made fun of others for his different looks and never understood the meaning of having a friend. this mockery and loneliness continues so much that at the age of 26, he decided to never leave the castle again and says: "The Black-Well family has been like a black stain on a white paper and nothing, no one is going to get along with us."
